  description: "socket.setdefaulttimeout/__qualname__/__len__()==17 / getdefaulttimeout/__qualname__/__len__()==17 / inet_aton/__qualname__/__len__()==9 / inet_ntoa/__qualname__/__len__()==9 — 'setdefaulttimeout' and 'getdefaulttimeout' are 17 chars each; 'inet_aton' and 'inet_ntoa' are 9 chars each; no prior socket spec checks __qualname__.__len__() for any of these functions; first __qualname__.__len__ anchor for setdefaulttimeout/getdefaulttimeout/inet_aton/inet_ntoa"
  kind: python_call_eq
